text: Clare Cathcart (3 October 1965 - 4 September 2014) was a Northern Irish actress. She appeared in the television series New Tricks, Call the Midwife and Doctors. She also appeared in Holby City, Father Ted and The Bill. Cathcart was born in Bellanaleck, County Fermanagh. Cathcart died from an asthma attack on 4 September 2014 in Brighton, East Sussex.
